==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: adynamic
<hw>ad`y*nam"ic</hw> <pr>(⟦acr⟧d`⟦icr⟧*n⟦acr⟧m"⟦icr⟧k)</pr>,
<pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F. <ets>adynamique</ets>. See
<er>Adynamy</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>Pertaining
to, or characterized by adynamia; weak.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> + <source>AS</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Physics)</fld> <def>Characterized by the absence of
power or force.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Adynamic fevers</b></col>, <cd>malignant or putrid fevers
attended with great muscular debility.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Adynamy</ent>⟦br⟧
